<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1>Bloccitoff</h1>
  <br>
  <p>Bloccitoff is a simple web app that allows you to create a list of things to do. Every item that is added to the list must be completed within 7 days. If you complete them before then, you can mark them as done. Otherwise, they will be automatically wiped after that time.</p>
  <p>
  <br>
  <% if current_user %>
    Go to your <%= link_to "account", current_user %>
  <% else %>
     <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-info' %> or
     <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-info' %> today!
  <% end %>
  </p>
</div>
